Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Mythologie Andromeda Perseus – und – Andromeda."

  • Extracts from different publications
  • Essay: 'H. G. Evers, Perseus und Andromeda von Rubens', in "Das Werk des Künstlers", n. 3/4, 1941/42
  • Bibliographic references
  • Photos of engravings and paintings ('Andromeda and Perseus', etc.)
  • Draft text "Perseus und Andromeda von Rubens"
  • List of artworks
  • Subfolder (Annotation: "Perseus und Andromeda"):
    • Correspondence with the director of the Staatlichen Schlösser und Gärten (Berlin) dated 1943
    • Extracts from different publications
    • Bibliographic references
